{"tid":753082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北捷色狼伸手摸女臀 靚仔相","createTime":"2018-07-23T10:24:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-23T11:59:11.000Z","uid":72009,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d1488cd18830fb874f65f739ab0c164a53180762","tid":753082,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T10:24:40.000Z","msg":"今早9時許，1名女子搭乘台北捷運文湖線要到內湖上班，她一進入車廂內就發現有一名年約20餘歲的年輕男子行為可疑，不斷朝她靠近，她感覺怪異立即遠離該男，並暗中觀察該名男子，不料，她發現該男子竟朝鄰近的女子下手，該男背對被害女子，表情佯裝無事，左手卻往後伸，數次刻意摳摸後方被害女子臀部，讓這名目擊女子非常生氣，趕緊拿起手機錄影蒐證。<br />\n<br />\n待捷運停靠後，目擊女子立即上前告知被害女子（23歲）已錄下證據，2女按下緊急通話鈕，摸臀男子則倉皇逃逸。被害女子事後向警方報案，指稱在搭乘捷運文湖線時，在松山機場站附近即感覺有人刻意觸摸她左臀，事後得知有目擊女子拍下證據，隨即持影像向警方報案。<br />\n目擊女子的丈夫則將該段錄影上傳到臉書《爆料公社》，氣憤表示，「老婆日常上班，捷運內湖線怪手男子，影片內容已轉交被騷擾的女孩，兩個女孩儘管按了車廂服務鈴，到站後還是被這個噁心男子烙跑」，文末更痛罵該男，「欠肉搜欠吉，馬的有夠噁，人模人樣手臂粗壯不會自己擼？」<br />\n該文章引來大批網友義憤，紛紛在底下留言，「噁」、「變態」等語罵聲不斷，也有網友留言怒斥，「看片看到腦袋都燒了」、「真大膽，這樣拍應該不是偷摸一次而已了」、「男性之恥、垃圾人渣」，也有人支持被害女子發現後應轉頭抓住該男，所幸目擊民眾拍下影片供被害女生向警方報案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20180723/1396865\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20180723%2F1396865&d=ZxeHy217KvZL1YY2zO4x2U%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=5ee97baa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20180723%2F1396865&h=4d622ff1\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20180723/1396865</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180723/640_aec6030ea89eac4afcd6cfb3e246f0cf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180723%2F640_aec6030ea89eac4afcd6cfb3e246f0cf.jpg&h=3f8cfd3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf45245685bc7e5865689c42fd3f8ce296d25210","tid":753082,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T10:40:18.000Z","msg":"有得甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11d983bde6fcb80994181d66414737801797ce31","tid":753082,"uid":14244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T10:52:48.000Z","msg":"幫人抆屎呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd79726839a8c3840fd28c92901b6e05212dd39f","tid":753082,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T10:54:02.000Z","msg":"邊位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aa04a60b5038b18e92b4bdbb4fe18e55a32f2e6","tid":753082,"uid":190928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T11:21:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9362da8baf48ccbb57ec4d2ee2ca39477fa9042","tid":753082,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T11:48:55.000Z","msg":"女人累人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da85d136a260cb5e571bef0804f07b75668818ee","tid":753082,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T11:51:04.000Z","msg":"如果是正妹，佢可以忍了好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c3d7b8a03a0877a233b0ec445feddc8ef119eec","tid":753082,"uid":119778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T11:59:11.000Z","msg":"台灣不意外"}]}